  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013880/extras/196f6a3927acd3e05b6995dde22f6404.poster.avif?t=1727737636\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013880/extras/196f6a3927acd3e05b6995dde22f6404.webm?t=1727737636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013880/extras/196f6a3927acd3e05b6995dde22f6404.mp4?t=1727737636\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Fight Risk is a minimalistic desk job game where you play as an air traffic controller trying to save a rogue flight. Master the communication systems before it's too late, or just wing it and see what happens!<br><br><strong>This is a SHORT game about deciphering systems and interactions. You will fail many times before you succeed.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> ~20-45 minutes of gameplay; depending on the player<br></li><li> Mixed 3D and text-based graphics<br></li><li> Retro 1980s aesthetic<br></li><li> Master air traffic computers<br></li><li> Translate flight codes<br></li><li> Navigate difficult terrains<br></li><li> Keep your pilot safe</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013880/extras/196f6a3927acd3e05b6995dde22f6404.poster.avif?t=1727737636\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013880/extras/196f6a3927acd3e05b6995dde22f6404.webm?t=1727737636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013880/extras/196f6a3927acd3e05b6995dde22f6404.mp4?t=1727737636\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Fight Risk is a minimalistic desk job game where you play as an air traffic controller trying to save a rogue flight. Master the communication systems before it's too late, or just wing it and see what happens!<br><br><strong>This is a SHORT game about deciphering systems and interactions. You will fail many times before you succeed.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> ~20-45 minutes of gameplay; depending on the player<br></li><li> Mixed 3D and text-based graphics<br></li><li> Retro 1980s aesthetic<br></li><li> Master air traffic computers<br></li><li> Translate flight codes<br></li><li> Navigate difficult terrains<br></li><li> Keep your pilot safe</li></ul>",
